**GUARANTEE**

If you're at Day 45 and nothing has changed, the 60-day guarantee is here. If you decide this approach isn't right for your child, you get every dollar back. No questions. No hoops.

But before you make that call: try the three checks above for one more week. Sometimes all it takes is a small adjustment.

